Name: Excessive 103s
Description: More than six 103 (accident) events detected for the unit in the last hour

Name: Excessive 127s
Description: More than ten 127 (last known location) events detected for the unit in the last 15 minutes

Name: Excessive zeros
Description: More than fifty (0; 0) locations (no GPS fix) detected for the unit in the last hour

Name: Future dated location
Description: Future dated location reported by the unit

Name: Invalid coordinates
Description: Invalid (out of bounds of South Africa) coordinates reported by the unit

Name: Identical coordinates
Description: More than five identical coordinates reported by the same unit in the last hour
